title: AVTECH Room Alert 32E: Sensor Temperature
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/environment/avtech
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the internal temperature
 and the temperature of sensors connected to
 a AVTECH Room Alert 32E device.
 Upper and lower levels as well as the display
 unit can be configured via WATO.

item:
 "Internal" for the device sensor and "Sensor X"
 for connected sensors where X=1-8 is the ID
 connected sensor.

inventory:
 One service is created for the internal sensor and
 one service is created for each sensor that delivers temperature data.
